    "description": "Mahindra Navistar International Enterprises invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Warehouse Manager at our Pimpri-Chinchwad location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Mahindra Navistar International Enterprises:\nMahindra Navistar International Enterprises is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mahindra Navistar International Enterprises!",
